  "text": "The Firefox Servo-based CSS style system resolution pipeline in layout/style/ consists of the following core files:\n\n1. **ServoStyleSet.h** (`layout/style/ServoStyleSet.h`) — Declares the `ServoStyleSet` class, the main entry point for style resolution. It is backed by a Servo Stylist and manages the set of StyleSheets that apply to a document. Key methods include `RuleAdded`, `RuleRemoved`, `RuleChanged`, `MediumFeaturesChanged`, `EvaluateSourceSizeList`, and `IsInServoTraversal`. It is a friend of `RestyleManager`.\n\n2. **ServoStyleSet.cpp** (`layout/style/ServoStyleSet.cpp`) — The implementation of `ServoStyleSet`, providing the actual style resolution logic including constructor/destructor and all style computation methods.\n\n3. **ServoBindings.h** (`layout/style/ServoBindings.h`) — Declares the Gecko-to-Servo FFI (Foreign Function Interface) functions. Described as 'FFI functions for Gecko to call into Servo', it uses macros to declare `extern \"C\"` functions such as `Servo_StyleSet_*RuleChanged`, `Servo_CssRules_Get*RuleAt`, `Servo_CounterStyleRule_GetDescriptorCssText`, and `Servo_CounterStyleRule_SetDescriptor`. These are the C-linkage bindings that allow C++ Gecko code to call into the Rust Servo style engine.\n\n4. **RestyleManager.h** (`layout/style/RestyleManager.h`) — Declares the `RestyleManager` class, which schedules and manages style recalculation. It also declares the helper class `ServoRestyleState` used to pass restyle state during traversal. Key methods include `PostRestyleEvent`, `ProcessRestyledFrames`, `ContentInserted`, `ContentWillBeRemoved`, and `GetRestyleGeneration`. It is a friend of `dom::Document` and `ServoStyleSet`.\n\n5. **ServoUtils.h** (`layout/style/ServoUtils.h`) — Declares utility functions for Servo traversal state, including `IsInServoTraversal()` (an inline function checking the `sInServoTraversal` global), `InitializeServo()`, `ShutdownServo()`, and `AssertIsMainThreadOrServoFontMetricsLocked()`. These utilities allow Gecko code to safely branch based on whether a Servo style traversal is currently in progress.\n\n6. **moz.build** (`layout/style/moz.build`) — The Mozilla build system file for `layout/style/` that lists all style system source files. It enumerates exported headers (including `ServoStyleSet.h`, `ServoBindings.h`, `RestyleManager.h`, `ServoUtils.h`, etc. under `EXPORTS.mozilla`) and compiled sources (including `ServoStyleSet.cpp`, `RestyleManager.cpp`, `GeckoBindings.cpp`, etc. under `UNIFIED_SOURCES`)."
